"{\"uid\": \"scmp.com-week-asia-lifestyle-culture-article-3274232-singapores-kitefoiling-set-soar-after-olympic-medal-win-wave-interest\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Kitefoiling, a more advanced form of kitesurfing, uses wind energy from a kite to pull the rider along.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 103, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Kitesurfing is believed to have been invented in the 1970s but only gained popularity in the 1990s.\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The sport featured at the 2018 Youth Olympic Games and in 2021, it was announced that kiteboarding would make its Olympic debut in Paris 2024 with the Formula Kite class that utilises hydrofoils.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 336, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999679547505, \"rank\": 3.204523669149725e-08, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 364, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.4954684021035498e-21, \"text\": \"Kite\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kite\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since Maximilian won Singapore's sole medal in the Olympics, interest in the sport has surged in the city state.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 514, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 408, \"end\": 418, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"score\": 0.9232458644177755, \"rank\": 0.05122598823449394, \"text\": \"Maximilian\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maximilian_I_of_Mexico\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore\